  <Dialog id="0" name="MSG_000_0_0" type="Message">
    <Page spk="0000"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 1181 0 -1 -1 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 1 0 0}{f 5 21 0 1}No words can express the sense of loss we feel as a result of this terrible tragedy.[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
    <Page spk="0000"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 1181 0 -1 -1 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 2 0 0}{f 5 21 0 1}He had a lifetime of opportunity ahead of him...[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
    <Page spk="0000"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 1181 0 -1 -1 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 3 0 0}{f 5 21 0 1}As educators, we are to blame for ignoring his silent calls for help.[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
    <Page spk="0000"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 1181 0 -1 -1 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 4 0 0}{f 5 21 0 1}We tragically lost him to senseless violence before we had a chance to help him realize his true potential...[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
    <Page spk="0000"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 1181 0 -1 -1 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 5 0 0}{f 5 21 0 1}Forgive us... Forgive us for our negligence...[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
  </Dialog>
