  <Dialog id="4" name="MSG_004_0_0" type="Message">
    <Page spk="0003"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 3 1 1 0 0 8 0 0}{f 5 21 0 2}He just never stops talking...[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
    <Page spk="0003"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 3 1 1 0 0 9 0 0}{f 5 21 0 2}I'd never even heard of any Aragaki, had you?[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
  </Dialog>
  <Dialog id="5" name="MSG_005_0_0" type="Message">
    <Page spk="0004"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 3 1 1 0 0 10 0 0}{f 5 21 0 3}I heard he never came to school. Probably just some punk.[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
    <Page spk="0004"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 3 1 1 0 0 11 0 0}{f 5 21 0 3}Ugh, I just wanna get home. I gotta study for my mock exam.[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
  </Dialog>
  <Dialog id="6" name="MSG_006_0_0" type="Message">
    <Page spk="0003"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 3 1 1 0 0 12 0 0}{f 5 21 0 2}Hey, you guys know who this Aragaki is?[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
    <Page spk="0003"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 3 1 1 0 0 13 0 0}{f 5 21 0 2}Wait, you're not even in the same year. No way you'd know him then.[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
    <Page spk="0003"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 3 1 1 0 0 14 0 0}{f 5 21 0 2}Anyways, it's crazy that stuff like this really happens, huh?[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
  </Dialog>
  <Dialog id="7" name="SEL_007_0_0" type="Selection">
    <Option><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}I wouldn't really know.]]></Option>
    <Option><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}You're just not aware of it.]]></Option>
    <Option><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}Shut your mouth.]]></Option>
  </Dialog>
  <Dialog id="8" name="MSG_008_0_0" type="Message">
    <Page spk="0003"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 3 1 1 0 0 15 0 0}{f 5 21 0 2}Oh, no? Man, no one seems to know anything.[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
    <Page spk="0003"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 3 1 1 0 0 16 0 0}{f 5 21 0 2}Geez, when is this gonna end? I don't have time for this.[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
  </Dialog>
  <Dialog id="9" name="MSG_009_0_0" type="Message">
    <Page spk="0003"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 3 1 1 0 0 17 0 0}{f 5 21 0 2}...Huh?[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
    <Page spk="0003"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 3 1 1 0 0 18 0 0}{f 5 21 0 2}Well, whatever. I was just asking...[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
  </Dialog>
